Notebowl


























































Our StoryThe world of higher education is changing.



Students are more concerned today about costs, and the real value of the education they’re receiving. Online alternatives and skill focused training programs are popping up everywhere, leading prospective students to ask, is college worth it?Our answer to that question is yes. College is incredibly important. We built Notebowl to help keep it that way.During our college experience, we saw the need to improve systems that were being used to manage the classroom experience, and connect students to campus life. Notebowl makes college more valuable by improving classroom experience, building community, enabling greater access to university network and connections, and opening up more career related opportunities.










