Company Overview of Notebowl Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Notebowl Inc. operates an online platform to broadcast lectures and save answers to student questions. Its platform integrates Google Calendar and iCal into a calendar that enables students to filter their calendar by event type that includes academic, personal, social, etc. The company also offers push notifications; creates private groups to study for a test, work on a class project, or communicate with friends on Google Hangouts and Instant Messenger; and offers campus life solution for bulletins, documents, assignments, grades, and class roster. In addition, it provides a mobile application. It serves students and professors. Notebowl Inc. was founded in 2011 and is based in Scottsdale, ...
Notebowl Inc. operates an online platform to broadcast lectures and save answers to student questions. Its platform integrates Google Calendar and iCal into a calendar that enables students to filter their calendar by event type that includes academic, personal, social, etc. The company also offers push notifications; creates private groups to study for a test, work on a class project, or communicate with friends on Google Hangouts and Instant Messenger; and offers campus life solution for bulletins, documents, assignments, grades, and class roster. In addition, it provides a mobile application. It serves students and professors. Notebowl Inc. was founded in 2011 and is based in Scottsdale, Arizona.
Detailed Description


